<view class="overlay" wx:if="{{visible}}" animation="{{animate}}">
  <view class="modalbox" style="top:{{top}}px">
    <view class="coins">
      <span><em>咚豆</em><var>{{coins}}</var></span>
    </view>
    <view class="tip">
      <span>咚豆可以用来解锁关卡、获得提示、跳过题目</span>
      <span>获得咚豆的方法：</span>
      <span>1. 分享给好友，得 10 个咚豆</span>
      <span>2. 分享到群，得 100 个咚豆</span>
    </view>
    <view class="controls">
      <button class="button" hover-class="active" open-type="share">
        <span> 分 享 </span>
      </button>
      <button class="button" hover-class="active" bindtap="close">
        <span> 关 闭 </span>
      </button>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>